		<div class="comment-body"><p>I really enjoyed the interview, but I think I cringed a little also at the &#8220;dixieland&#8221; comments. He made some good points that I can&#8217;t disagree with but I would point out just how resourceful us Southerners can be. Everyone around here is a jack of all trades and does damn near everything themselves. And yes, we&#8217;re fiercely independent but we also bend over backwards to help our neighbors. We just don&#8217;t get too touchy/feely about it. That said, I liked the guy and hope he comes back again.</p>
