		<div class="comment-author vcard">
			<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/7d2936c345d695cda92e4624438ca504?s=48&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />
			<cite class="fn">Post Carbon</cite>

